Shaderkit is an OpenGL shader development environment.

Shaderkit is free software and released under the GNU GPL 3 license (see COPYING).

Building
--------
To build Shaderkit, run the following commands
```
qmake .
make -j2
```
Assuming the dependencies are installed, this should result in the Shaderkit binary being built.

